Haywire;;41;;80;;R;;Mallory Kane (Gina Carano) is a highly trained operative for a government security contractor. Her missions take her to the world's most dangerous areas. After Mallory successfully frees a hostage journalist, she's betrayed and left for dead by someone in her own agency. Knowing her survival depends on learning the truth behind the double-cross, Mallory uses her black-ops training to set a trap. But when things go awry, Mallory knows she'll die unless she can turn the tables on her adversary.;;Action,Mystery & thriller;;Steven Soderbergh;;2012;;Gina Carano,Michael Fassbender,Ewan McGregor,Bill Paxton,Channing Tatum,Antonio Banderas,Michael Douglas,Michael Angarano,Anthony Brandon Wong,Aaron Cohen;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/haywire_2011